Class TempSetting

java.lang.Object
  twcore.core.command.TempSetting
Direct Known Subclasses:
BoolSetting, DoubleSetting, EnumSetting, IntSetting, PlayerSetting, StringSetting
abstract class TempSetting
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract TempSetting all specific types of settings must extend. Provides name storage and individual locking functionality.
